messages.messageBody:
Well, get yourself over to Mr. Bruhn's school. :) He'll let you try out a
class if you want to get a feel for things. Tomorrow is not a good day -- it's
belt party day. OTOH, maybe you could come and just hang out and meet people --
like me. :)

The name of the school is K.C. Chung and the phone number is 561-220-8249.
The address is 259 SW Monterey Road (at the foot of the Palm City bridge). Feel
free to write me at marbleface@... if you want directions or anything. Or
give me a call.

Nance


In a message dated 6/15/2004 4:28:12 AM Eastern Daylight Time,
unschoolingbasics@yahoogroups.com writes:
Hi Nance

We would love to find a good program and we ARE in your area. We are
actually in Florida Unschoolers :) My son was in a great program
before but the program has changed since he was involved.

Thanks

Cheryl
